events.event_name: Release of RatingDog China General Composite PMI (January 2026)
events.description: The RatingDog China General Composite PMI rose to 51.6 in January 2026, marking a 3-month peak.

facts.fact_text: The RatingDog China General Composite PMI rose to 51.6 in January 2026 from 51.3 in the previous month.
